Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥 在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥 你到底在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥 不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.38,0:02:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍…劍…劍心嗚嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.02,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十二話\N化淚水為勇氣 小薰的抉擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個王八在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連個招呼也不打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一聲不響就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.10,0:03:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 拜託你別衝動\N可別砸壞了店裏的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好可怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.67,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不揍那個死劍心一拳\N我這口氣是不會消的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 好啊 你最好跟著去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則 再這樣下去 店會被你搞砸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但沒有錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說啥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 小氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.42,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要來借錢 就不要弄壞人家的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.73,0:03:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法嘛 不拿些東西出氣\N心情平靜不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子竟不遵守約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有我的同意 你可不能私自去流浪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在發飆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 即便如此\N劍心還是重回武士之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來以為他會在小薰家 住下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰不知如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.83,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有看到左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊 剛才還在我家亂發飆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 小薰現在怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.64,0:04:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 總是一副無精打彩的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心好像是 當面對她道再見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用不著擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.07,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大家的照顧 再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能瞭解他的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是窩在一旁 那不是他的做風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其這兩天 更是連句話都不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 你們兩個要為小薰打打氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些錢應該足以到京都了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思 回來一定還你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我的信用不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不敢奢望 把手伸出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餞別的禮物 拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是小型的炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.71,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 你又做出這種怪東西啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是新造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 這是用來護身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你可要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的京都 可是超乎你想像的危險地帶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.06,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道志志雄的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可別小看我新聞記者 情報綱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可別洩漏此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.03,0:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方可是黑社會一大勢力\N不會輕易放過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會洩漏出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正也不會有人相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.38,0:06:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的亡靈要對這個國家\N展開復仇之類的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 絕不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候你還在幹嗎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.76,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰不大妙 光憑我一個人無法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 你被跟蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.67,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是京都嘍 不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 被你這種膽小鬼跟來 真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.78,0:06:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道對方的弱點 是戰術中基本的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.55,0:06:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們若去京都 志志雄一定也會跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.45,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但以現在的拔刀齊 根本無法保護你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他才決定一個人去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.39,0:07:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對拔刀齊而言\N你們只會成為他的包袱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 我只是劍心的負擔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怕無法顧到我 而一個人出走的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說了那麼多 你們還不明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.14,0:07:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去京都必定全軍覆沒 那不是你們的地盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖待在東京吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.49,0:07:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽你說了這番話 我更想揍那傢伙一拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開 齊藤 否則我就使勁衝過去嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就回敬你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.48,0:07:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙 太低級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.08,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛剛就一直盯著 他肩膀剛好的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.59,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說了嗎 捉住敵人的弱點是戰術之基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既不卑鄙也不低級\N這兒可不流行什麼正正當當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都就是這樣的廝殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不是你們這些年輕小伙子來的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.17,0:08:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖的待在東京吧 聽到了沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.41,0:08:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要你們管 這點傷算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.35,0:08:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不痛 比起這…這點傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.23,0:08:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被劍心視為包袱 更是讓我痛心疾首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開 齊藤 我要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了京都我要用這拳頭\N證明我也能助那傢伙一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要用你的拳頭\N證明給我們看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真敢說呢\N前不久才慘敗我手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要被他激怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.53,0:09:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 這次就配合你\N赤手雙拳決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 別相信他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙手段卑鄙 不可掉以輕心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我真是不受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 我只用拳頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.41,0:09:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨瓜一個 還要人家配合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.38,0:09:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒想看看一個\N不自量力的傢伙慘敗的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是有趣 看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.89,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂打一通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助那小子 什麼時候學了那招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.63,0:09:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的拳法和先發制人恰恰相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是先接招再還手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 回敬對方招術之技倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不給你空間轉圓 我就贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂打幾拳總會中一拳 雖然不大好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.42,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 別讓我笑死了\N什麼回敬對方招術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎 怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣快的拳全都接住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一次都沒打中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.09,0:10:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再打幾拳也是沒用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拳的速度及力道並沒差太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.91,0:10:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我老是打不中\N而他卻可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖不甘心 但是真的是很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有他能和劍心平分秋色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和拔刀齊及我相較之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.74,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你既沒有實力也沒經驗 差我們太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.57,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們來說 你只是個會呱呱叫的小雞罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘍嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還能動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管誰阻止我 我都要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.19,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心 雖然他沒帶刀\N但那可是牙突招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助快閃\N挨了他一招可就糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快不行了吧\N下顎一擊已震至腳底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這小子能站是很勉強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你如何死命掙扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只不過是個小鬼罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你怎樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.29,0:12:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是小鬼\N傷你一雙手臂還難不了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 怕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.97,0:12:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和劍心能有今天 絕非一日所成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以也別輕視我這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.14,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.84,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再和你這種人混\N只是浪費時間和體力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想去京都就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好趕快被殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.92,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自視天生的強勢\N而不知保身的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是活不了多久的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你贏了 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不用安慰我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 對了 趕快包紮傷口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是右肩的傷 不好好處理的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 王八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖擊拳卻一次也沒\N打到我肩膀的傷處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連第一次的發拳\N還故意錯過我的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.60,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是配合我在比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.57,0:13:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是壬生之狼\N新撰組三番隊長的實力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 剩下的就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.28,0:13:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要把小姐 帶到劍心那兒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堅強點 要撐住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.00,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對拔刀齊而言 你們只是他的包袱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.83,0:13:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到京都為止 我一定要撐住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰如何了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得舒服些了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不在耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底去哪兒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.89,0:14:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服披在那呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼應該還在家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是追不到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.22,0:14:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時劍心的一句再見\N束縛了我整個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 齊藤和左之助都好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管小薰如何阻止 我也要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.53,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要守著道場 不能去京都啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.77,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼 小薰也還在道場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖做得不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但什麼都不吃的話 對身體不好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是小燕特地為你做的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 你要消沉到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.22,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點 吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不吃就不吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.50,0:16:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要管我 拜託讓我一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了你 怎麼還待在這兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.17,0:16:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是來嘲笑這個 被劍心甩了的可憐女啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高…高荷 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把我和只會哭哭啼啼的人混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會懂的 現在我什麼都不想做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.69,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都不想做 你現在最盼望的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就去找他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.80,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怕被劍心冷冰冰的對待是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我家的祖傳秘方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.58,0:16:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前 劍心還誇說很有效呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在劍心一定很需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.75,0:16:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給你這個愛哭鬼也沒用\N還是叫禰彥帶去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.65,0:16:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心看到這個 一定會想起我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道會把你丟哪去嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此 你就別麻煩別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己送去京都不是更好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉 我可不像你那麼閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一堆病人在等我呢\N我怎能說走就走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.94,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些病人比劍心還重要是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對劍心的心意 也只不過如此嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 你說得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我 我可也是出身名師門下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家 都好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才別小看我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了償還我的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我選擇了醫生一途 救助更多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎 這是我的生存之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而告訴我這個道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是別人 就是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.25,0:17:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我死了 殺人者無法再復生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但比起那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.02,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人為了救更多的人而揮劍 才是真的贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人斬拔刀齊正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起拔刀齊的劍 高荷你純熟的醫術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能救更多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 行醫去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.20,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為所有因毒藥 傷痕 病痛所苦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,付出你的心力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.01,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 不管發生什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使劍心不在世上 我也要貫徹救人之使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.85,0:18:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也正是向劍心 傳達了我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.36,0:18:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想被你這種 只會畏縮一旁的人說教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會躲在一旁哭哭啼啼的愛哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊 真是天真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 你不會懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.47,0:18:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種當面說再見的悲傷 你絕對不會懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我也不見得好到哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.71,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連再見都沒有跟我說一聲\N這樣的心情你不會瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.49,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要說話前 請先想清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 我一定會帶劍心回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不要哭了 乖乖等我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連再見都沒有跟我說一聲\N這樣的心情你不會瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.71,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠…其實想馬上就去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在磨蹭什麼啊 快準備啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.05,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.39,0:20:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心只有向你說再見 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對劍心來說 和你分離是最難過的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎 只有你能把劍心帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不在時 小惠會看著道場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你則要用你的雙手 將這個交給劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答啊 小薰 難道你不想見劍心一面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.62,0:20:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.52,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我想…見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…好想…見劍心一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 就這樣決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去京都吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.80,0:23:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.53,0:23:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也都踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空無一人的道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然出現了一位 帶著過往傷痕的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.84,0:23:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要來和劍心一決勝負
